 lo\u1ea1i gia\u0300u dinh d\u01b0\u01a1\u0303ng, tho\u00e1t n\u01b0\u1edbc t\u1ed1t. T\u1ea1i Vi\u1ec7t Nam, c\u00e2y thanh t\u00fa c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 tr\u1ed3ng r\u1ed9ng r\u00e3i kh\u1eafp c\u00e1c v\u00f9ng mi\u1ec1n. V\u00e0 c\u00e2y cho hoa quanh n\u0103m.<\/p>\n<p>C\u00e2y thanh t\u00fa v\u1edbi hoa m\u00e0u xanh \u0111\u1eb9p l\u1ea1 n\u00ean th\u01b0\u1eddng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng tr\u1ed3ng ph\u1ed1i k\u00e9p v\u1edbi c\u00e1c c\u00e2y th\u00e2n th\u1ea3o kh\u00e1c nh\u01b0 c\u00e2y c\u1ea9m t\u00fa mai ho\u1eb7c c\u00e2y l\u00e1 m\u00e0u \u0111\u1ec3 tr\u1ed3ng vi\u1ec1n t\u1ea1o nh\u1eefng l\u1ed1i \u0111i \u0111\u1ea7y hoa c\u1ecf trong s\u00e2n v\u01b0\u1eddn ho\u1eb7c khu c\u1ea3nh quan \u0111\u00f4 th\u1ecb.<\/p>\n<p>C\u00e2y thanh t\u00fa c\u00f2n hay \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tr\u1ed3ng t\u1ea1o th\u1ea3m d\u01b0\u1edbi nh\u1eefng b\u1ea3ng hi\u1ec7u c\u1ed5ng ng\u1ecf c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c t\u00f2a nh\u00e0, nh\u00e0 m\u00e1y c\u00f4ng ty. Hoa xinh x\u1eafn, xanh l\u1ea1 n\u1edf quanh n\u0103m t\u1ea1o n\u00ean kh\u00f4ng kh\u00ed vui t\u01b0\u01a1i, m\u00e1t d\u1ecbu cho c\u1ea3nh quan khu\u00f4n vi\u00ean<\/p>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>T\u00ean khoa h\u1ecdc: Evolvulus alsinoides, Evolvulus glomeratus H\u1ecd th\u1ef1c v\u1eadt: Convolvulaceae (B\u00ecm b\u00ecm) C\u00e2y thanh t\u00fa c\u00f2n [&#8230;]\n","protected":false},"featured_media":571,"comment_status":"open","ping_status":"closed","template":"","meta":[],"product_cat":[99],"product_tag":[],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"http:\/\/cayxanh.websiteviet.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/product\/570"}],"collection":[{"href":"http:\/\/cayxanh.websiteviet.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/product"}],"about":[{"href":"http:\/\/cayxanh.websiteviet.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/product"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"http:\/\/cayxanh.websiteviet.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/comments?post=570"}],"wp:featuredmedia":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"http:\/\/cayxanh.websiteviet.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media\/57